import { FormControl, FormLabel, VStack } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import React from 'react'

const Signup = () => {
  return (
    <VStack spacing="5px">
      <FormControl>
         <FormLabel></FormLabel>
         <Input
            placeholder="Ente"
         />
      </FormControl>
    </VStack>
  )
}

export default Signup
